kquote><br />\n佢跟本唔當係娛樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實佢都意識到但要選擇繼續我都冇計"},{"pid":"ff4880ada85fe9ad2f340b0890903ecc7d431bab","tid":114371,"uid":8650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T18:25:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Same<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我個問題唔係係打機到<br />\n好想留低但係每到夜晚諗完一輪又好想走<br />\n矛盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日都係到諗"},{"pid":"320a882955d4c532983796d9d7b573172bf23a61","tid":114371,"uid":8650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T18:27:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>照直好嚴肅咁同佢講，俾佢知你好認真<br />\n真係無改變/佢意識唔到就<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講個問題？咁耐以黎真係講到口臭，已經知道佢會點答我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8fec08e8f876dc4faa8d5d7c2d11e891755da0d","tid":114371,"uid":7149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T18:47:51.000Z","msg":"呃唔到自己 到最後冷淡收場仲哂時間"},{"pid":"d5be1e438bbe578418809192071ff380c501407e","tid":114371,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T18:49:09.000Z","msg":"叫佢咪再打機啦<br />\n拍拖係要令大家都有目標 一齊變好呀"},{"pid":"84ef7fc731a728e60bdfa4a1083f054c128ef979","tid":114371,"uid":63062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T18:57:54.000Z","msg":"睇到上面好多留言同回覆。<br />\n<br />\n樓主講過離離合合左幾次，我想問係咪每次都因為打機？<br />\n如果係的話，咁你男朋友真係byebye得，佢同電腦過世啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果唔係的話，我諗個問題唔係在於男方打幾耐機，而係佢會因好小事就嬲左樓主，咁我只可以講佢未夠成熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我男朋友曾經都好易為小事嬲同發脾氣，<br />\n最後一次鬧交我衝口而出話佢好唔成熟，<br />\n之前一直無講因為我怕佢可能會hurt親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<br />\n點知嗰次佢好似搵左朋友傾計，開左曉咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講左咁多其實唔知你係咪都一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果類同希望你男朋友早日諗通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bbd3184e190737e88eb7746e13502d789d40328","tid":114371,"uid":60810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T19:03:26.000Z","msg":"打機都咁 以後返工比人鬧 生活有壓力睇黎絲打都幾唔得閒下"},{"pid":"69a5e152c04366e42e23dd33e63890a24638639d","tid":114371,"uid":8650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T19:13:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呃唔到自己 到最後冷淡收場仲哂時間</blockquote><br />\n我都唔知要用幾多時間去沖淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55d94c2252a1ab9a75da76b9bceaad4267447d81","tid":114371,"uid":8650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T19:13:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫佢咪再打機啦<br />\n拍拖係要令大家都有目標 一齊變好呀</blockquote><br />\n佢肯就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e2d223603b12904fba181be7d5d6344a9519e77","tid":114371,"uid":8650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T19:16:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇到上面好多留言同回覆。<br />\n<br />\n樓主講過離離合合左幾次，我想問係咪每次都因為打機？<br />\n如果係的話，咁你男朋友真係byebye得，佢同電腦過世啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果唔係的話，我諗個問題唔係在於男方打幾耐機，而係佢會因好小事就嬲左樓主，咁我只可以講佢未夠成熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我男朋友曾經都好易為小事嬲同發脾氣，<br />\n最後一次鬧交我衝口而出話佢好唔成熟，<br />\n之前一直無講因為我怕佢可能會hurt親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<br />\n點知嗰次佢好似搵左朋友傾計，開左曉咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講左咁多其實唔知你係咪都一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果類同希望你男朋友早日諗通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一時三刻好難解釋到我同佢嘅狀況，但多謝你打咁大段野同我講<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"314adf3bfe20aec46b3f0cb54bed5339c66ebfb6","tid":114371,"uid":8650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T19:17:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打機都咁 以後返工比人鬧 生活有壓力睇黎絲打都幾唔得閒下</blockquote><br />\n佢係好大壓力果啲人，但唔識減壓"},{"pid":"e7699cae68a1426f25c4f88ee4b3317abe81d387","tid":114371,"uid":3645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T23:40:31.000Z","msg":"好認真，我以前都係打機鬧女朋友啲人嚟，呢啲行為唔係叫愛自己，而係冇氣出，攤出嚟講清楚 慢慢過多段時間 佢就會知 之後改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"042f760e364268fdb29cf52605f4b468095bb84b","tid":114371,"uid":83215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T23:42:56.000Z","msg":"哈哈我條女打lol都係咁鬧我，利申我垃圾五佢鑽石<br />\n後尾我用左外掛先跟到佢步伐<br />\n不過宜家我地兩個都無打機嚕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1086fd49fb2647cc3273cf7e3f3b742f7b196a6","tid":114371,"uid":83215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T23:44:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>哈哈我條女打lol都係咁鬧我，利申我垃圾五佢鑽石<br />\n後尾我用左外掛先跟到佢步伐<br />\n不過宜家我地兩個都無打機嚕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我應該係唯一一個打機比條女鬧既人😂"},{"pid":"fdb033e5f3b46ddd87aa44cb8804430b285e5a2f","tid":114371,"uid":13361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T23:46:38.000Z","msg":"打機唔理條女 早日分手啦<br />\n結左婚仲慘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4c59e4b5f961e4371c83a2e676d8fd28d6d3b34","tid":114371,"uid":50718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T00:17:38.000Z","msg":"我同你調番轉 不過我做左d更過分既野 我唔想再搞到佢喇 由我自己毒撚過世算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f99fd3c212e1acb5f340916a0ab41646e50825e6","tid":114371,"uid":48705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T00:23:54.000Z","msg":"唔明點解話要搵左自己先分手喎 咁嘅情況都分得啦"},{"pid":"b134db1f1bb1fa2718ec4b01f92e110ee8032ab5","tid":114371,"uid":83709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T00:42:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cece07c26e736a2a5c2806d7ef0e7513933c263e","tid":114371,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T00:57:43.000Z","msg":"「係時候啦！不要再見！」"},{"pid":"4cc6b1e84e2bf984c19f4acc3a318ce2afa5f134","tid":114371,"uid":8650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T07:58:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔明點解話要搵左自己先分手喎 咁嘅情況都分得啦</blockquote><br />\n我唔捨得一刀兩斷，成個世界唔同曬，所以諗住比自己小小時間去準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81bd96f1969ea7c8d334306bee36c6f9f4dda133","tid":114371,"uid":8650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T07:59:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>哈哈我條女打lol都係咁鬧我，利申我垃圾五佢鑽石<br />\n後尾我用左外掛先跟到佢步伐<br />\n不過宜家我地兩個都無打機嚕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我應該係唯一一個打機比條女鬧既人😂</blockquote><br />\n我都想佢可以唔打"},{"pid":"b03b8ac4526399a706cdec60ca32ec74716b0a92","tid":114371,"uid":47005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T08:28:09.000Z","msg":"成個世界唔同晒&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n咁你趁佢打機唔理你時候，慢慢建立番你自己的世界<br />\n<br />\n出去識多d 人，男好女好，培養自己興趣，喜歡做乜就做乜<br />\n<br />\n到佢擠到少少時間理下你，你咪俾番少少時間理下佢，跟住返去自己世界<br />\n<br />\n到一日，自然講得出分開了"},{"pid":"91c7ae3c27767132be22abe6d83db5f8388be236","tid":114371,"uid":14492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T09:52:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>斷斷續續都拍左四年，散過幾次又一齊返<br />\n我好愛佢好想同佢走到最後，但我發現佢口講話愛我其實淨係愛自己，永遠自己係最重要<br />\n為打機可以屌到我盡，問佢呢啲野係咪值得發我咁大脾氣佢話係<br />\n果下我終於肯面對現實，雖然好痛<br />\n我應該點做，點講分手，點面對身邊一切都有同佢嘅回憶？<br />\n真係好痛，但始終要面對現實。。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n絲打 我想問下 當初點樣可以分左一次復合返"},{"pid":"2693056f1adfacb9a210b4baedab28851de861ad","tid":114371,"uid":83215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T10:01:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>哈哈我條女打lol都係咁鬧我，利申我垃圾五佢鑽石<br />\n後尾我用左外掛先跟到佢步伐<br />\n不過宜家我地兩個都無打機嚕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我應該係唯一一個打機比條女鬧既人😂</blockquote><br />\n我都想佢可以唔打</blockquote><br />\n用外掛陪佢玩la"},{"pid":"f0d3b12f944d43048aab920c64971b6c7bf661f3","tid":114371,"uid":74153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T01:54:50.000Z","msg":"我唔知你地仲有冇其他野<br />\n<br />\n但分手唔可以咁易講<br />\n你地已經散過再一齊 <br />\n係好難得<br />\n<br />\n睇下有幾多人講左呢啲再收唔番既說話既巴絲<br />\n<br />\n唔好咁易講呢句<br />\n<br />\n我都覺得你試下諗下佢點解咁講先 <br />\n唔好咁諗住<br />\n其實佢都可能只係想做番自己<br />\n所以先會咁<br />\n你試下苦口婆心咁同佢講想佢改下啲態度/問題<br />\n因為一齊咁耐真係唔容易"},{"pid":"90907864ab5953e19da11236df85f085fc630379","tid":114371,"uid":56912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T02:01:03.000Z","msg":"講分手，然後del晒佢所有既野，喊左2個星期， 再去一個長trip<br />\n返黎就重新開始<br />\n利申，試過"},{"pid":"67aee63697824e63e563a9d8b4f7e5bbb611e76c","tid":114371,"uid":62862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T02:02:40.000Z","msg":"我都係拍左4年拖 好想講分手 但好唔捨得<br />\n琴日女朋友承認鐘意咗第二個 <br />\n我明知落去都無意思 但開唔到口講分手<br />\n呢種感覺好難受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80206ed1961279e2d65d8ffab5f12ec67cf1c9b8","tid":114371,"uid":1327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T02:21:02.000Z","msg":"應該早分早著 你諗下同呢d 人結婚會點<br />\neq 又低 自制能力又低 野又做唔到 成世對住佢咩<br />\n唔好浪費時間係呢d 人到 <br />\n你唔係果個令佢覺醒既人<br />\n或者大家既下個會更好<br />\n佢搵到令佢覺醒既人<br />\n你搵到照顧得你更好的人"},{"pid":"0f492f1e6420f80e98d7815c690d75a0c2ee8857","tid":114371,"uid":56682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T03:07:43.000Z","msg":"第時結埋婚家暴都似。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7325d028fef84b2a0a8c69714a5b2506c165390","tid":114371,"uid":80832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T03:10:07.000Z","msg":"四年就長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5c468484642940f5e92840d726345f862953c8e","tid":114371,"uid":18889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T03:23:00.000Z","msg":"愛人前應學會自愛<br />\n但自愛不等於會愛人<br />\n很多情人太自我中心<br />\n分手事因而變得十常八九 <br />\n<br />\n不值得你愛的人就一腳踢開他 不用留戀"},{"pid":"6f40e785dc4861ade97283e178b1a7ae13fb78af","tid":114371,"uid":29489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T03:57:21.000Z","msg":"其實唔駛講分手的<br />\n<br />\n你唔搵佢 就自然分開<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：過來人"}]}